 THE Hyundai
crashed into a lamp post on Sunday. According
to Trauma Response Africa, the horrific car crash happened in the early hours
of Sunday morning, on Oliver Tambo Road close to Falck Street in Bloemfontein. The driver was
alone in the car when it crashed. “Paramedics
arrived on the scene to find the driver had already succumbed to his injuries
and that there was nothing more that could be done to save him,” Trauma
Response Africa said. He was
declared dead on the scene, and cops opened an inquest docket and will be
investigating the cause of the accident.  